2. How to use this code?
-------------------------
 To use this code You will need git program installed if You want to
 clone this repo and make own patch to the project, or simply download
 it by clicking at ZIP button at the top of Github page, to download
 zip package with all files.

 After download it just compile the code using 'make' command.
 Makefile will generate the hex file, which You can programm into MCU
 using 'make program' command. Makefile using avrdude software to push
 the hex file inside the AVR.

 Yo can clean the code using 'make clean'.
    
3. Fuse bits
-------------
 In CONFIG file You can find fuse values.
 To set the fuse bits in MCU, You have to run in example:

 > avrdude -c usbasp -p atmega8515 -U lfuse:w:0x1f:m
 > avrdude -c usbasp -p atmega8515 -U hfuse:w:0xd9:m

